des: "This is a great pancake mix to have on hand for a quick breakfast. My kids love them and all of the variations we create. I feel better knowing what ingredients are in them."
ins: Whisk all-purpose flour, oat flour, whole wheat flour, buttermilk, wheat germ, baking powder, baking soda, and salt in a large bowl until well blended. Store in an airtight container for up to 6 months.
